&lt;p&gt;Wexham Park Hospital has an exciting opportunity for an experienced nurse or registered professional with a valuable interest in safe discharge and patient flow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wexham is part of Frimley Health ICS, our ICS covers a large footprint over East Berkshire and South Buckinghamshire - we are looking for a highly motivated, creative and experienced clinical manager to continue to drive our health and social care teams within Wexham Park Hospital. This role is very influential within our system and requires good management and leadership skills to continue to manage multiple tasks on a daily basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy problem solving and providing high standard of care for our patients please apply for your next great opportunity working within this successful team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Heidi Barber&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Head of Site&lt;/p&gt;
